{{ fields.description or '—' }}

## People
- Assignee: {{ fields.assignee.displayName or '—' }}
- Reporter: {{ fields.reporter.displayName or '—' }}

## Project
- Project: {{ fields.project.key }}
- Components: {% if fields.components and fields.components.length %}{% for c in fields.components %}{{ c.name }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}{% else %}—{% endif %}
- Fix Versions: {% if fields.fixVersions and fields.fixVersions.length %}{% for v in fields.fixVersions %}{{ v.name }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}{% else %}—{% endif %}
- Labels: {% if fields.labels and fields.labels.length %}{{ fields.labels | join(', ') }}{% else %}—{% endif %}

